                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="contoh-kalimat-asking-opinion-dan-giving-opinion-beserta-arti-dan-masing-masing-10">
                            1. Contoh kalimat asking opinion dan giving opinion beserta arti dan masing-masing 10</h2><br />
                        <p>Giving: i think itu Will be better of you used the red long dress</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="buatlah-10-kalimat-dari-asking-opinion-dan-giving-opinion-beserta-artinya%e2%80%8b">
                            2. Buatlah 10 kalimat dari asking opinion dan giving opinion beserta artinya​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>1. In my opinion...</p><p>    Menurut pendapatku...</p><p>2. I think...</p><p>    Aku pikir...</p><p>3. I believe that...</p><p>    Aku percaya kalau...</p><p>4. From my point of view…</p><p>    Dari sudut pandangku…</p><p>5. I reckon...</p><p>    Aku pikir...</p><p>6. I feel like...</p><p>    Aku merasa...</p><p>7. To be honest...</p><p>    Sejujurnya...</p><p>8. I suppose...</p><p>    Menurutku...</p><p>9. As far as I’m concerned…</p><p>     Sejauh yang aku perhatikan…</p><p>10. I suggest...</p><p>      Aku menyarankan...</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="10-contoh-kalimat-my-opinion">
                            3. 10 contoh kalimat my opinion?</h2><br />
                        <p>Here's the example of saying your opinion</p>I think the food here is delicious.I suppose the team has done well this season. In my opinion, this job is very challenging. I believe the task is not for today. I'd say this project is not easy to do.If you ask me, I'd say they won't stop till they get what they want. I think this is very unusual event.I believe the world is not getting any better. In my view, the time is not right for that. I'd say the break time is too long.<p></p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>Saying an opinion is one of the main expression in our daily life and surely in the daily conversation. In saying opinion, one can say in various ways. Here they are</p>I think...I believe...I'd say ( I would say).....In my view,....In my opinion,....I suppose......<p></p><p><strong>Pelajari lebih lanjut: </strong></p><p>Saying an opinion</p><p>brainly.co.id/tugas/2305954</p><p></p><p><strong>Detail Jawaban: </strong></p><p>Kelas: SMP</p><p>Mapel: English</p><p>Kategori: Saying opinion</p><p>Kode: 8.5.1</p><p>Kata kunci: saying opinion </p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="buat-percakapan-mengenai-giving-opinion-10-kalimat%e2%80%8b">
                            4. buat percakapan mengenai giving opinion 10 kalimat​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>papapapapapappaap</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>bababababababaabbabaabBba</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="apa-saja-kalimat-perhatian-opinion">
                            5. Apa saja kalimat perhatian opinion?</h2><br />
                        kalimat yang sifatnya belom terjadi <br />1. "i think"  <br /> 2. "in my opinion is' <br />
