                        giving opinion ; i think your sister very beautiful..... asking opinion : what do you think about my school?contoh ujaran kalimat ;<br />1 "What do you think about our class?"<br />2. what do you opinion my bag<br />3. what do you think about my new pencil case<br />4. what do you think my new laptop<br />5.whats your opinion about my dress<br />6.what do you think my house<br />7. what do you think my new classroom<br />8. what do you opinion my new shoes<br />9. what do you think my new hat<br />10. what do you think my school<br />dialonya :<br />a : hai how are you<br />b ; i am fine thank you and you<br />a; i am fine too, by the way yesterday my perents from to aceh they buy me a new laptop , what do you think my new laptop ?<br />b; i think its very cool<br />a ; thank you<br />b; youre welcome<br /><br /><br /><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="membuat-dialog-tentang-opinion-dan-responya-minimal-10-kalimat%e2%80%8b">
