                        <p>liza: Hey Fira good morning</p><p>Fira:Good morning Liza whats the problem</p><p>Liza: do you know we are going to make a video about our activity in ppkm?</p><p>Fira: yeah i know it</p><p>Liza: well since you are my chair mate what are you thinking about it?</p><p>Fira:Well i feel upset a bit about it,to be honest i dont really do much in ppkm.and the duration must more than 5 minute! are you feel the same as me?</p><p>Liza: oh okay it means our opinion is not match,i think its a good lesson, i cam express myself much more when it comes to video</p><p>Fira:Oh well good for you</p><p>Liza:How about we make it together in my house?</p><p>Fira:that sounds great</p><p></p><p></p><br />
