                        kalau expression opinion = this cake is really delicious &amp; kalau responding opinion = no,i dont think so. itu contoh yaa. =)<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tuliskan-kalimat-asking-opinion-dan-giving-opinion">
                            9. Tuliskan. Kalimat asking opinion dan giving opinion </h2><br />
                        <p>Asking opinion : What do you think about my new cut hair?</p><p>Giving opinion : I think it is too short.</p><br /><p>2) Asking opinion : Do you have any idea?</p><p>Giving opinion : I think we should ask our teacher before doing this project.</p><br /><p>3) Asking opinion : Do you have any opinion on her idea?</p><p>Giving opinion : I think it is a good idea.</p><br /><p>4) Would you give me your opinion on my painting?</p><p>Giving opinion : I personally feel that your painting is very attractive. I love its color.</p><br /><p>5) Asking opinion : How was the trip?</p><p>Giving opinion : If you ask me, I think I don't like it. It is so boring.</p>asking :what do you think about? (bgmn pendapatmu?) <br />giving:I think that.. (saya berfikir bahwa...)<br />somoga membantu mf klo slh<br />
