                        In my opinion, Bambang Pamungkas is one of famous football player in Indonesia.~ I think we must study from now to be a honored person<br />~ I think Deidara is the cutest one in Naruto movie<br />~ In my opinion, a lion is the most vicious animal <br /><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="kalimat-yang-menunjukan-kalimat-giving-opinionasking-opinion-dan-respond">
                            32. kalimat yang menunjukan kalimat giving opinion,asking opinion, dan respond</h2><br />
                        giving : what can i do for you ?<br />asking : you can help me ?<br />respond : yes , suregiving = This book is very colorfull<br />asking = what do you think of Bandung?<br />respond = ok. Thank you for your opinion<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="10-contoh-kalimat-giving-opinion">
                            33. 10 contoh kalimat giving opinion</h2><br />
                        <p>Below are the <strong>examples of giving opinion</strong></p><strong>In my opinion, </strong>kids need to play more in the outdoors.<strong>Personally, I think </strong>the movie was not that great.<strong>From my point of view</strong>, she does not do anything wrong.<strong>According to my opinion, </strong>the sales number should have been higher.<strong>I believe </strong>that he won't neglect his family.<strong>I strongly believe </strong>that<strong> </strong>the government should provide free healthcare for everyone.<strong>To me</strong> religion is the most important thing.<strong>I think </strong>this place is nice.<strong>To be honest</strong>, the food is too pricey.<strong>If you ask me, I think </strong>I don't like the blue paint for bedrooms.<p><strong></strong></p><strong>Pembahasan</strong><p><strong>Frasa </strong>yang tercetak tebal pada jawaban di atas, merupakan <strong>ekspresi</strong>-ekspresi yang dapat digunakan untuk memberikan pendapat dalam bahasa Inggris. Di bawah ini adalah <strong>contoh </strong>lain untuk ekspresi mengungkapkan <strong>opini</strong>:</p>In my humble opinion...To/in my mind…From my perspective…According to me…As far as I am concerned...<p>Giving opinion atau memberikan pendapat dapat diekspresikan kepada seseorang yang bertanya maupun tidak. Terdapat kebebasan untuk mengungkapkan pendapat kita asalkan kita menyampaikannya secara <strong>baik</strong>/<strong>sopan</strong>. Di era digital ini, banyak masyarakat yang menyalahgunakan sosial media untuk memberikan opini mereka kepada orang lain di internet secara tidak baik.</p><p><strong></strong></p><strong>Pelajari lebih lanjut</strong>Materi tentang 10 soal pilihan giving opinions https://brainly.co.id/tugas/23040842Materi tentang contoh kalimat general opinion https://brainly.co.id/tugas/23814883Materi tentang expressing opinion https://brainly.co.id/tugas/18255252<p></p>Detail jawaban<p><strong>Kelas:</strong> 8</p><p><strong>Mapel:</strong> Bahasa Inggris</p><p><strong>Bab:</strong> Expression for attention, asking and stating opinion, checking on understanding and expression of appreciation</p><p><strong>Kode:</strong> 8.5.1</p><p></p><p><strong>#AyoBelajar #SPJ2</strong></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="carilah-10-kalimat-tentang-giving-opinion-beserta-artinya-%e2%80%8b">
                            34. Carilah 10 kalimat tentang giving opinion beserta artinya ​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>J</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>w</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>b</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>:</strong></p><p><strong>Giving opinion (memberi atau merespon pendapat)</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>P</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>r</strong><strong>t</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>y</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>:</strong></p><p><strong>I think you should obey your parents. ...</strong></p><p><strong>I think you should obey your parents. ...In my opinion, this book is good enough. ...</strong></p><p><strong>I think you should obey your parents. ...In my opinion, this book is good enough. ...From my point of view, we need to do small research. ...</strong></p><p><strong>I think you should obey your parents. ...In my opinion, this book is good enough. ...From my point of view, we need to do small research. ...Based on my opinion, you should go there. ...</strong></p><p><strong>I think you should obey your parents. ...In my opinion, this book is good enough. ...From my point of view, we need to do small research. ...Based on my opinion, you should go there. ...In my mind, you are right. ...</strong></p><p><strong>I think you should obey your parents. ...In my opinion, this book is good enough. ...From my point of view, we need to do small research. ...Based on my opinion, you should go there. ...In my mind, you are right. ...Honestly, this is so risky. ...</strong></p><p><strong>I think you should obey your parents. ...In my opinion, this book is good enough. ...From my point of view, we need to do small research. ...Based on my opinion, you should go there. ...In my mind, you are right. ...Honestly, this is so risky. ...I believe we will find a solution.</strong></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="contoh-kalimat-asking-opinion-dan-giving-opinion-masing-masing-5">
                            35. contoh kalimat asking opinion dan giving opinion masing masing 5</h2><br />
                        <p>Asking Opinion expression is an expression to ask other people's opinions on an issue.</p><p>Giving Opinion expression is to express an opinion on a matter or issue.</p>Pembahasan<p>Giving opinion sama dengan responding opinion.</p><p>Contoh kalimat asking opinion dan giving opinion yaitu</p><p>1. Asking opinion : What do you think about my new cut hair?</p><p>Giving opinion : I think it is too short.</p><p>2. Asking opinion : Do you have any idea?</p><p>Giving opinion : I think we should ask our teacher before doing this project.</p><p>3. Asking opinion : Do you have any opinion on her idea?</p><p>Giving opinion : I think it is a good idea.</p><p>4. Would you give me your opinion on my painting?</p><p>Giving opinion : I personally feel that your painting is very attractive. I love its color.</p><p>5. Asking opinion : How was the trip?</p><p>Giving opinion : If you ask me, I think I don't like it. It is so boring.</p>Pelajari lebih lanjut<p>Soal dan jawaban tentang asking opinion pada https://brainly.co.id/tugas/16083843</p><p>Contoh kalimat asking opinion dan giving opinion pada https://brainly.co.id/tugas/3059748</p><p>Dialog asking and giving opinion tiga orang pada https://brainly.co.id/tugas/948352</p><p>Opinion expressions pada https://brainly.co.id/tugas/8883774</p><p>-----------------------------</p>Detail Jawaban<p>Kelas: XI</p><p>Mapel: Bahasa Inggris</p><p>Bab: Can greed ever be satisfied? (Chapter 1)</p><p>Kode: 11.5.1</p><p></p><p>#JadiRankingSatu</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="berikan-contoh-kalimat-ungkapan-offer-dan-giving-opinion-masing-masing-10-contoh">
                            36. berikan contoh kalimat ungkapan offer dan giving opinion masing-masing 10 contoh</h2><br />
                        offer opinion:<br />1. What do you think about that building?<br />2. What your opinion about this book?<br />3. What do you think? Is English difficult or easy?<br />4. What do you think of the picture?<br />5. he's a dilligent student. don't you think so?<br />6. the meal is not delicious. is that how you say it?<br />7. what your opinion about that movie?<br />8. the movie is not interesting. is that how you say it?<br />9. What do you think about Indonesia?<br />10. What do you think about this celebrity?<br /><br />giving opinion: <br />1. yes, he did. it is very beautiful<br />2. that building is awesome. i like it<br />3. i don't think so. it's nice<br />4. yes, he is. he is dilligent and smart too<br />5. it think English is easy<br />6. I will use English in class<br />7. That novel was interesting. where did you buy it?<br />8. I did like that movie. it's romantic<br />9. Indonesia is rich<br />10. this celebrity is beautiful and smart too<br /><br />semoga berguna ya:)<br /><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="buatlah-10-kalimat-opinion-tentang-rumah-dalam-bahasa-inggris%e2%80%8b">
                            37. buatlah 10 kalimat opinion tentang rumah dalam bahasa inggris​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>i like my house</p><p>your house is big</p><p>my house have 3 room</p><p>my house is small</p><p>your house have 5 room</p><p>my house have no pool</p><p>your house have a big pool</p><p>i like your house</p><p>your house is cool</p><p>my house is cool</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p><strong>semoga terbantu</strong></p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tolong-buatkan-10-contoh-giving-opiniondan10-contoh-asking-for-opinion">
                            38. Tolong buatkan 
10 contoh giving opinion
Dan
10 contoh asking for opinion</h2><br />
                        Asking opinion.<br />1.) What do you think about my appearance today ?<br />2.) What do you think about this meatball ?<br />3.) What do you think about the math test ?<br />4.) What do you think about my clothes ?<br />5.) What do you think about my bicycle ?<br />6.) What do you think about my bag ?<br />7.) What do you think about my handphone ?<br />8.) What do you think about this chair ?<br />9.) What do you see in there ?<br />10.) What do you think about this book ?<br /><br /><br />Giving opinion.<br />1.) I think you're so beautiful today.<br />2.) I think this meatball is delicious.<br />3.) I think it is very difficult.<br />4.) I think your clothes is able with you.<br />5.) I think your bicycle is amazing.<br />6.) I think your bag is new.<br />7.) Wow, that's an amazing handphone.<br />8.) I think this is an old chair.<br />9.) I see an amazing circus in there.<br />10.) I think this book is interesting.<br /><br /><br />Maaf jika salah. Semoga membantu ^_^<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="kalimat-ungkapan-to-give-opinion-and-ask-opinion">
                            39. kalimat ungkapan to give opinion and ask opinion</h2><br />
                        asking opinion : what do you think about my new shoes? atau bisa juga what is your opinion about my shoes?<br /><br />giving opinion : i think your new shoes is cool, atau bisa juga in my opinion, your new shoes is cool <br /><br />cmiiw, semoga membantu yaa! <br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="contoh-kalimat-the-expression-of-opinion-responses-dan-membuat-kalimat-tentang-expression-of-opinion">
                            40. Contoh kalimat the expression of opinion responses dan membuat kalimat tentang expression of opinion</h2><br />
                        <p>Asking:<br />Formal(-have you got any comments on....<br />             -do you have any idea?<br />             -what is your opinion about.......?)<br />Informal:(-what do you think of....?<br />               -what do you think about....?)<br />Giving:formal(-i personally believe....<br />                  -i personally consider....<br />                  -i personally think...<br />Informal(-i think I like it<br />               -i think that....<br />               -in my opinion...</p><br />
                    
